data.title: The Enlightener
data.meta_description: The Enlightener (2010) starring Lukman Sardi, Slamet Rahardjo, Zaskia Adya Mecca and directed by Hanung Bramantyo.
data.text: The journey of an Indonesian national hero named K.H. Ahmad Dahlan striving for Muhammadiyah, an Islamic organization in Indonesia, and how he was rejected by the society as he was trying to fix up their perspective.
